sqlView.name: Stock Balance - Descendents
sqlView.description: Query for aggregating all latest events from stock program for ou mode descendents
sqlView.sqlQuery: select de.name ,sum(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(tedv.value, '0'), '[^0-9]+','0' ,'g')::integer) as value from programstageinstance psi inner join( SELECT psi.organisationunitid,max(psi.executiondate),max(psi.programstageinstanceid) as psiid FROM programstageinstance psi inner join programstage ps on ps.programstageid = psi.programstageid where ps.uid like 'tjFzBT4dKBE' and psi.organisationunitid in (select organisationunitid from _orgunitstructure ous where uidlevel${level} like '${ouuid}') group by psi.organisationunitid )latestEvent on latestEvent.psiid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join trackedentitydatavalue tedv on tedv.programstageinstanceid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join dataelement de on de.dataelementid = tedv.dataelementid where de.uid in ('YCphYFZA8YG','coNVUUsyLcl','ex0fnpbdMnN','rczOvUL6XdS','JcGcvIplsiL','LG7LZuHdxWi') group by de.name

sqlView.name: Stock Balance - Selected
sqlView.description: Query for getting the latest event from stock program for ou mode selected
sqlView.sqlQuery: select de.uid,de.name,sum(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(tedv.value, '0'), '[^0-9]+','0' ,'g')::integer) as value from programstageinstance psi inner join( SELECT psi.organisationunitid,max(psi.executiondate),max(psi.programstageinstanceid) as psiid FROM programstageinstance psi inner join programstage ps on ps.programstageid = psi.programstageid where ps.uid like 'tjFzBT4dKBE' and psi.organisationunitid in (select organisationunitid from organisationunit where uid='${ouuid}') group by psi.organisationunitid )latestEvent on latestEvent.psiid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join trackedentitydatavalue tedv on tedv.programstageinstanceid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join dataelement de on de.dataelementid = tedv.dataelementid where de.uid in ('YCphYFZA8YG','coNVUUsyLcl','ex0fnpbdMnN','rczOvUL6XdS','JcGcvIplsiL','LG7LZuHdxWi') group by de.uid,de.name

sqlView.name: org
sqlView.sqlQuery: SELECT organisationunitid, uid,name from organisationunit where name like 'Maramba%' or name like 'Victoria%' or name like 'Linda%' or name like 'Simoonga%' or name like 'Mahatma%' or name like 'Libuyu%' or name like 'Southern%' or name like 'Livingstone%' or name like 'Zambia%'

sqlView.name: Stock Balance - Children
sqlView.description: Query for aggregating all latest events from stock program for ou mode children
sqlView.sqlQuery: select de.name,sum(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(tedv.value, '0'), '[^0-9]+','0' ,'g')::integer) as value from programstageinstance psi inner join( SELECT psi.organisationunitid,max(psi.executiondate),max(psi.programstageinstanceid) as psiid FROM programstageinstance psi inner join programstage ps on ps.programstageid = psi.programstageid where ps.uid like 'tjFzBT4dKBE' and psi.organisationunitid in ( select organisationunitid from organisationunit where parentid = ( select organisationunitid from organisationunit where uid='${ouuid}') or uid='${ouuid}' ) group by psi.organisationunitid )latestEvent on latestEvent.psiid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join trackedentitydatavalue tedv on tedv.programstageinstanceid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join dataelement de on de.dataelementid = tedv.dataelementid where de.uid in ('YCphYFZA8YG','coNVUUsyLcl','ex0fnpbdMnN','rczOvUL6XdS','JcGcvIplsiL','LG7LZuHdxWi') group by de.name

sqlView.name: test
sqlView.sqlQuery: select de.name,executiondate,sum(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(tedv.value, '0'), '[^0-9]+','0' ,'g')::integer)as value from programstageinstance psi inner join( SELECT psi.organisationunitid,min(psi.executiondate),min(psi.programstageinstanceid) as psiid FROM programstageinstance psi inner join programstage ps on ps.programstageid = psi.programstageid where ps.uid like 'tjFzBT4dKBE' and psi.organisationunitid in ( select organisationunitid from organisationunit where parentid = ( select organisationunitid from organisationunit where uid='DQjaNvP9ulw') or uid='DQjaNvP9ulw' ) group by psi.organisationunitid )latestEvent on latestEvent.psiid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join trackedentitydatavalue tedv on tedv.programstageinstanceid = psi.programstageinstanceid inner join dataelement de on de.dataelementid = tedv.dataelementid where de.uid in ('YCphYFZA8YG','coNVUUsyLcl','ex0fnpbdMnN','rczOvUL6XdS','JcGcvIplsiL','LG7LZuHdxWi') group by de.name, psi.executiondate
